metadata.name: CAN’T STOP by JED X’O
metadata.description:
Can’t Stop aka The JGEDNESIS is a song that I wrote when I was  neglected by family and friends because I decided to pursue a career in Music. It’s my first ever song release and I’m glad to have launched it on the blockchain. This song was brought to life as a result of real time connections I made with other Artists across continents through web3 Twitter spaces; from the artwork to the production of the beat and even the M&M. 

Holders of The JGEDNESIS  gets exclusive access to the JEDIVERSE(a community that I’m building with friends and supporters) 

This song was made to inspire you to keep at your dreams regardless of whatever challenges you might be facing.  

Always remember why you do what you do, keep your eyes on the price and never let your obstacles put you off because without obstacles, one can’t achieve greatness. 
CAN’T STOP TILL YOU GET TO THE TOP.
